
say \\\弹药装填

say 将子弹和用合成的方式装填入空弹匣中，放在副手，主手持枪持续  长按/右键 进行换弹

say 如果合成栏位置不够，可以通过 副手持有子弹 主手持有弹匣持续 长按/右键 装填弹药

say 已装好的子弹可以直接在合成栏扣出子弹

say \\\武器使用

say 武器决定的是 稳定性，射程，射速，而伤害完全由子弹决定。

say 通过 长按\右键  开枪

say 通过 蹲下 打开瞄准镜，开启瞄准镜后，你可以更好的操控枪支，子弹的散布范围会下降

say 通过 快速点击俩次 蹲下 查看装填的弹药种类以及剩余弹量

say 通过 头部视角垂直看着地面，这样你无法射出子弹，适用于长按换弹的时候，以防走火

say \\\健康系统

say 你的生命值不会自然恢复,你只能够通过 使用恢复生命值的药物来进行治疗

say 当你的经验值每提升10级,你的生命上限会提升两颗,最高只能提升10颗.

say 在蹭到铁丝网时会得到大出血效果，生命值低于7点会骨折，受到部分怪物的攻击，也会有各种各样的负面效果。

say 通过持续 长按\右键 使用药品来治疗自己

say 受伤后可能会得到各种各样的负面效果，列如骨折，大出血，不同的药物底下会详细的说明能治疗哪些效果，在治疗骨折效果时，请保证你的生命值大于7

say \\\生存操作指南

say 在对局内容器可以搜索到 问号图标 的物品，将它放在背包，就会自动随机生成杂物。

say 藏身处的大部分功能需要耗电，列如 开灯，挖掘虚拟数字货币，电网防御等等

say 初始安全箱 可以容纳一定量的物品，处于安全箱的物品死亡后不会掉落。

say 在藏身处，会有笔记本电脑，并且上面写着SHOP，通过将物品摆在上面的九宫格完成出售物品

say 在藏身处的1楼，会有一排展示框，通过 右键\长按 打开交易栏，购买物品

say \\\敌人

say 当你离敌人足够近时，未处于潜行状态，会直接引起敌人的注意，可以通过潜行来降低被发现的概率
say 当敌人附近没有敌对目标时，会尝试治疗自己


say \\\Ammo Loading 
say Load bullets into an empty magazine by combining them.Place the magazine in your off-hand and hold the gun in your main hand. Press and hold the right mouse button to reload. 
say If there isn't enough space in the crafting grid,you can load ammo by holding bullets in your off-hand and the magazine in your main hand, then press and hold the right mouse button. 
say Loaded bullets can be directly removed from the crafting grid. say\\\Weapon Use 
say Weapons determine stability,range, and fire rate, while damage is entirely determined by the bullets. 
say Press and hold the right mouse button to fire. 
say Crouch to open the scope.When aiming down sights, you can control the gun better, and bullet spread is reduced. 
say Double-tap the crouch button quickly to check the loaded ammunition type and remaining ammo count. 
say Look vertically at the ground with your head to prevent firing.This is useful when holding down the right mouse button to reload, avoiding accidental discharge. say\\\Health System 
say Your health does not regenerate naturally.You can only heal by using medical items that restore health. 
say For every 10 levels of experience you gain,your maximum health increases by 2 hearts, up to a maximum increase of 10 hearts. 
say Touching barbed wire will cause heavy bleeding.If your health drops below 7 hearts, you will suffer fractures. Some monster attacks can also inflict various negative effects. 
say Use medical items by pressing and holding the right mouse button to heal yourself. 
say After being injured,you may suffer various negative effects such as fractures or heavy bleeding. Different medical items specify which effects they can treat. When treating fractures, ensure your health is above 7 hearts. say\\\Survival Operation Guide 
say In the game,you can search containers for items with a question mark icon. Place them in your inventory, and they will automatically generate random loot. 
say Most functions in the hideout require electricity,such as turning on lights, mining virtual currency, and activating电网防御. 
say The initial safety box can hold a certain number of items.Items in the safety box will not drop upon death. 
say In the hideout,there is a laptop with "SHOP" written on it. Place items in the 3x3 grid on it to complete item sales. 
say On the first floor of the hideout,there is a row of item frames. Right-click or hold to open the trade menu and purchase items. say\\\Enemies 
say When you are close enough to an enemy and not in stealth mode,you will immediately alert them. You can reduce the chance of being detected by sneaking. 
say If there are no hostile targets nearby,enemies will attempt to heal themselves.